public abstract class AbstractComboBox.EditorComponent
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements javax.swing.ComboBoxEditor

The EditorComponent is the one that used as editor. If you want to create your own EditorComponent that can be used in AbstractCombo, you should always extend this class. It has nothing but a value. Subclass should implement stringToObject which can convert from the text to the actual value.
